  "response": "Rahul Gandhi is an Indian politician and a member of the Indian National Congress (INC) party. He was born on June 19, 1970, to Rajiv Gandhi and Sonia Gandhi. Both his father and grandmother, Indira Gandhi, served as Prime Ministers of India. Rahul Gandhi has been involved in politics for many years, taking on various roles within the INC, and has been elected as a Member of Parliament multiple times. His involvement in politics is often seen as part of his family's legacy, as the Nehru-Gandhi family has been a prominent political dynasty in India for several generations.",
